== Simple Server Status ==

== joet3ch [joe@t3ch.com] ==

=Description=
Monitor the connectivity to various services and display results in web ui

=Requirements=
web.py [ http://webpy.org/ ] (test with v0.34)

=Setup=
- Create database 'sss' using the 'schema.sql' file
- Add database details to 'config.py'
- Add cron job for 'launch.py'
- Run app 'python sss.py' (add to your system's startup)

=Usage=
- add/modify services in the database table 'sss.services'
- navigate to http://<your_ip>:8080/ 
